title: Wal-Mart Names Brett Biggs CFO To Replace Charles Holley, Who Is Retiring
text:
Published By: Fox Business - Today 
Wal-Mart Stores Inc. said Friday it has appointed Brett Biggs as its new chief financial officer to replace Charles Holley, who is retiring....
